originalText.text: So I left my car here and let the guy parked for us. After we left we didn’t ask for the key since we think that the key should be in somewhere like the cup holder or the bin on the door. We notice we cannot find the key after we stopped at a place for some food. We looked literally everywhere in the car include the trunk and even the space for spare tire. After looking for more than 2 hours, we found out that the key was at the engine. HOW CAN YOU PUT THE KEY AT THE ENGINE!!! we got lucky that the key did not drop since we found the key after driving 2 hours on the freeway.
